It all started as a Meme when 20-year old Matty Roberts from california posted a internet joke on facebook called "Storm Area 51, They Can't Stop All of Us" and afer that it went viral.
More than 3.5 million people were willing to atttend the Area 51 raid on September 20 where Matty Roberts posted about storimg the secret military facility thinking to expose and discover the aliens the government hid.
Turns out its a Top-secret milotary facility based at the desert in the Groom Lake in the southern side of Nevada located in the United States.
Now people are inspired to visit the desert base in Nevada after the viral event " area 51 raid" happened. 
